{"tid":2360090,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Lady Gaga呼籲彈劾特朗普 期望取消未來參選資格","createTime":"2021-01-09T12:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T16:44:28.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"37093f9528a72a9948be6b66fc222a9fd23c5285","tid":2360090,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普的支持者因不滿選舉結果，於大前日衝擊國會大樓引發騷亂，結果造成5人死亡。樂壇天后Lady Gaga前日在Twitter發文呼籲彈劾特朗普，及取消他未來的參選資格。<br />\n<br />\nLady Gaga留言指騷亂是恐怖主義：「我希望我們能集中彈劾特朗普，讓國會有憲法的權力去取消他將來參選的資格。第25條修正案並沒有取消他資格。他煽動國內的暴力，還需要發生多少暴力事件？這是恐怖主義。」雖然特朗普卸任在即，但有部份議員仍希望透過彈劾以阻止他日後的參選資格。倘若彈劾通過，參議院便可表決禁止他於2024年再次參選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/noMesec5oZ7l2cIh36chMJNSs6Q=/802x499/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TVPGZYU4JZEBVFJKIEEGFO2E64.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnoMesec5oZ7l2cIh36chMJNSs6Q%3D%2F802x499%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTVPGZYU4JZEBVFJKIEEGFO2E64.JPG&h=621817c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210109/FHALMXEBAVGE3IVBHLXU6UAETA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210109%2FFHALMXEBAVGE3IVBHLXU6UAETA%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDXyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=0917b834\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210109%2FFHALMXEBAVGE3IVBHLXU6UAETA%2F&h=9d2f4811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210109/FHALMXEBAVGE3IVBHLXU6UAETA/</a>"},{"pid":"41efffa0aa50a8d7d7cb1fb082e6ae3b5874fedf","tid":2360090,"uid":272819,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:01:49.000Z","msg":"DQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如俾中共管曬地球啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor